Insider Activity


Individual




Joseph Truitt



Mr. Joseph Truitt is Chief Commercial Officer & Executive VP at Achillion Pharmaceuticals, Inc.
Mr. Truitt was previously employed as VP-Business Development & Product Strategy by Lev Pharmaceuticals, Inc., Vice President-Sales & Operations by Johnson & Johnson, and Vice President-Sales & Operations by OraPharma, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from LaSalle University and an MBA from St. Joseph's University.



